description: Link Prop Investment AB operates as a real estate investment company. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2015-07-02. The firm operates as a real estate property investment company with a focus on office space that indirectly owns, manages and leases the property Linkoping Idedebatten 3 in Mjardevi Science Park in Linkoping, Sweden. In addition, the Company provides investment opportunity for investors who do not normally invest directly in property. The firm is active in Sweden.
name: Link Prop Investment AB (publ)
